WEBVTT

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:32.376
and he read a line from a lost work

00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:34.720
of the Greek comic dramatist Menander.

00:11:35.760 --> 00:11:38.456
This was the first time
in well over a thousand years

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:41.040
that those words
had been pronounced aloud.

00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:44.440
In that moment, he became a scholar.

00:11:45.440 --> 00:11:48.320
Ladies and gentlemen,
that is the future of the past.

00:11:48.840 --> 00:11:50.056
Thank you very much.

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:53.080
(Applause)